{"version":3,"term":{"cols":80,"rows":24},"timestamp":1783505933,"idle_time_limit":2.0,"command":"bash /Users/tanmaydevare/Tanmay/DedrooM/dedroom/demos/demo3_quickstart.sh","env":{"SHELL":"/bin/zsh"}}
[0.017, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  DedrooM Quick Start Demo\r\n  =========================\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[1.008, "o", "  Step 1: Install (one pip command)\r\n  --------------------------------\r\n\r\n"]
[1.010, "o", "  $ pip install dedroom\r\n\r\n  That's it. No config files, no setup script.\r\n\r\n"]
[2.009, "o", "  Step 2: Start + route (eval init)\r\n  ---------------------------------\r\n\r\n"]
[1.006, "o", "  $ eval \"$(dedroom init)\"\r\n\r\n  Starts the proxy daemon in the background\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  and sets the env vars your agent needs.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Add the exports to ~/.zshrc for permanence.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[2.010, "o", "  Step 3: Use your agent normally\r\n  -------------------------------\r\n\r\n"]
[1.007, "o", "  $ claude              # Claude Code\r\n  $ codex               # OpenAI Codex\r\n  $ aider               # Aider\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  $ cursor              # Cursor (GUI)\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Everything routes through the proxy automatically.\r\n  Loop protection, compression, PII redaction —\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  all invisible to the agent and to you.\r\n\r\n"]
[2.008, "o", "  Step 4: Check what's happening\r\n  ------------------------------\r\n\r\n"]
[1.008, "o", "  $ dedroom status   # PID, uptime, tokens saved, healing stats\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  $ dedroom report   # Per-tool savings, top tools, waste\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  $ dedroom doctor   # Full diagnostics (11 checks)\r\n\r\n"]
[2.006, "o", "  Step 5: Stop\r\n  ------------\r\n\r\n"]
[1.008, "o", "  $ dedroom stop\r\n\r\n  Stops the daemon. No cleanup needed.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[2.006, "o", "  That's the full workflow:\r\n    pip install dedroom\r\n    eval \"$(dedroom init)\"\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    # ... use your agent ...\r\n    dedroom status\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    dedroom stop\r\n\r\n  All in one terminal. No new workflow to learn.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[1.009, "x", "0"]
